<br>
There are several npcs standing around to be killed.<br>
<br>
All are lvl 25, and can be pulled seperately.<br>
(One is 20, the one closest to the water on the right of the dock facing up the isle.)<br>
<br>
Lady on dock, lady beside tree.  (several are in houses, but they are a pain to pull seperate.) Little dorf by fire, the other one beside him is a vendor and won't attack you.<br>
Then 2 dorfs on the other side of the isle.<br>
<br>
They are great exp till they go green at 35.  I could(necro) solo atleast 2, sometimes 3-4(after my 34 spells.)  Just don't bite off more than you can chew.  2 is amazing exp.  I got 3 lvls in a weekend.  Since you are doing 2 and they react differently, it isn't as boring.<br>
<br>
oh. .DON'T USE FEAR.  Last thing you want is for the feared person to run right by the warrior guild leader. . she double hits for somewhere around 400. be sure to slow them too.<br>
<br>
Take a small group and you could probably kill all of them, and be constantly killing.  <br>
<br>
All are about a 6 min spawn. <br>
<br>
(edit)<br>
Hit for about 52.  Bash, kick, double attack, dual wield. Warriors.  <br>
<br>
The wood elfs drop purity belts, rusty weapons, not much else i can think of. plat upwards of 3-4.<br>
